#

Pork Tenderloin Salad

40 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A hearty and refreshing salad featuring tender pork, vibrant greens, and a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • avocado: 1
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
